    .intro
      .container.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
        h2 Use cases
        p Discover number of ways in which your business can benefit from our suite of Conversational Bots. We have used industry best practices to curate templates to get you up and running quickly.
        p All our templates come with AI Models , NLP, Machine Learning and domain specific conversational workflows.
