            .hiring__features__block__btn
              a(href="#")
                i.icon.icon-play
                | See video
              a(href="pdf/Outreach Bot.pdf" target="_blank") Read more
                i.icon.icon-arrow-right
          .hiring__features__block
            img(src="img/landing-home/landing-home_features_img-8.png", alt="")
